## `app/(tabs)/(home)/index.tsx` (Android/Web — 823 lines)
A **separate** home screen inside `(home)/` group. For **clients**: shows logo, greeting, a red "Post a New Gig" button (`router.push('/post-gig')`), and a list of their posted gigs fetched from `/api/gigs/client/${user.id}`. For **providers**: shows available gigs from `/api/gigs/matches/${provider.id}`, separates direct offers (`selectedProviderId === provider.id && status === 'pending_acceptance'`) from regular open gigs, with Accept/Decline buttons. Has polling every 5s when direct offers exist.

